title: Dvoriste u prave dane leta 2015
text:
Only registered TrekEarth members may write critiques. Photographer's Note 
Dvoriste u prave dane leta 2015. Pogled na dvoriste u prve dane leta sa starim plugom, raznim starinama i kacom sa muljacom za grozdje. Stari gvozdeni plug, drveno bure i muljaca sada krase dvoriste. Dan je bio sa oblacima koji su doneli kisu. Yard in the first days summer of 2015. View of the garden in the first days of flight with the old plow, a variety of antiques and katz with crushers for grapes. The old iron plow, wooden barrel and crushers now adorn the yard. The day was the clouds that brought rain.
